    <main class="pt-24 pb-12">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 md:p-10">
          <h1
            class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-blue-600 text-center mb-4 quicksand"
          >
            Privacy Policy
          </h1>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-center text-sm mb-8">
            Last Updated: <span class="font-medium">October 2025</span>
          </p>

          <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            <section>
              <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">
                1. Introduction
              </h2>
              <p>
                Welcome to StudentTracker. This privacy policy explains how we
                collect, use, and protect your personal data when you use our
                platform. Your privacy is critically important to us, and we are
                committed to safeguarding your information.
              </p>
            </section>

            <section>
              <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">
                2. Information We Collect
              </h2>
              <p class="mb-2">
                To provide our services, we may collect the following types of
                information:
              </p>
              <ul class="list-disc list-outside pl-5 space-y-1">
                <li>
                  <strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, email address,
                  contact details, and other identifiers provided during account
                  registration.
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Student Academic Records:</strong> Information such as
                  grades, attendance records, class schedules, and other
                  performance-related data.
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Usage Data:</strong> We automatically collect
                  technical information, including IP address, browser type,
                  device information, and pages visited, to monitor and improve
                  our service.
                </li>
              </ul>
            </section>

            <section>
              <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">
                3. How We Use Your Information
              </h2>
              <p>
                We use the information we collect to operate and maintain the
                StudentTracker platform, provide personalized features, improve
                our services, communicate with you, and ensure the security of
                our systems.
              </p>
            </section>

            <section>
              <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">
                4. Data Protection
              </h2>
              <p>
                We implement industry-standard security measures, including
                encryption and access controls, to protect your data from loss,
                misuse, and unauthorized access. However, no method of
                transmission over the Internet is 100% secure.
              </p>
            </section>

            <section>
              <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">
                5. Your Rights
              </h2>
              <p>
                You have the right to request access to, correction of, or
                deletion of your personal data. You can also object to the
                processing of your data. Please contact us to make such a
                request.
              </p>
            </section>

            <section>
              <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">
                6. Contact Us
              </h2>
              <p>
                If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy,
                please do not hesitate to contact us at
                <a
                  href="mailto:me.sharma.amrit@gmail.com"
                  class="text-blue-600 hover:underline font-medium"
                  >me.sharma.amrit@gmail.com</a
                >.
              </p>
            </section>
          </div>
